00:53:21.850 --> 00:53:24.120
Or really bands from
two different orbitals

00:53:24.120 --> 00:53:25.004
jammed together.

00:53:25.004 --> 00:53:26.045
They happened to overlap.

00:53:28.690 --> 00:53:30.770
So as a consequence
here, if this

00:53:30.770 --> 00:53:33.760
