01:09:11.800 --> 01:09:17.390
And he did so with decisiveness
and dispatch and a head

01:09:17.390 --> 01:09:20.029
of almost all of
his-- in fact, I

01:09:20.029 --> 01:09:24.359
think all of his German-Jewish
physicist colleagues

01:09:24.359 --> 01:09:27.850
and those German physicists
for whom the Hitler

01:09:27.850 --> 01:09:29.297
